Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama ini, aku memaksa Marie\Nmelakukan berbagai macam hal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku sudah melakukan kejahatan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, apa itu karena aku tahu\Nkamu manusia?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa, jantungku berdetak\Nlebih cepat dari biasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku harus tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika aku panik, semua orang akan tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur juga bersikap aneh hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia masih sakit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku gugup saat berada di dekatnya.\NMereka akan tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menjauh dari Marie\Nuntuk hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.37,0:02:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bergadang\Nmenyusun dokumen untuk OSIS,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi aku agak lelah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku akan melayani Tuan Arthur\Ndengan baik hari ini
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan menghiburnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, berbaringlah\Ndi pangkuan saya seperti biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang sudah kulakukan pada\Ngadis manusia selama ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menatap...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, aku sedang tak mau\Nbantal pangkuan hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitukah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bantal pangkuan, dihindari.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, aku akan belajar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sulit sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika mau belajar,\NAnda butuh sesuatu yang manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya kebetulan memanggang\Nkue mangkuk sebagai camilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan dimakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini, buka mulut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa melakukannya jika dengan robot,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi bukankah ini akan membuat kami\Nseperti pasangan sungguhan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.\NAku akan makan kue mangkuk itu nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Disuapi, dihindari.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mengambil bukuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan belajar seharian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bisa mengabaikanku\Ndan melakukan apa yang kamu suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, saya akan beralih\Nke mode bersih-bersih.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:04:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersih-bersih, ya?\NTerima kasih, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, tolong mundur.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami menyamar sebagai pegawai\Nuntuk mendekatinya, tapi ketahuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pembersihan selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keren sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, jangan mengotori kaki Anda.\NBiar saya antar ke kamar Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak boleh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, kamu tidak hanya keren,\Ntapi juga sangat manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kamu mencoba membunuhku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hampir mati karena jantung berdebar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan saya.\NItu pasti menakutkan, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua yang saya lakukan hari ini\Nsepertinya menyusahkan Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku takut orang lain akan menyadarinya,\Njadi aku terus menolak kebaikan Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pasti terluka saat aku tiba-tiba\Nmemperlakukannya seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, Marie juga manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, itu tidak benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama kamu melakukan sesuatu untukku,\Naku akan bahagia apa pun itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedangkan aku hari ini,\Naku tampak agak aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, aku tak akan belajar hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, aku akan melakukan\Napa pun yang kamu mau.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bolehkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya aku mengatakannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bertahanlah, jantungku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur adalah manusia,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:06:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi saya yakin ada saatnya\NAnda tak mau dilayani.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya saya tak akan melakukan\Napa pun kepada Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, kenapa kita di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena di sini sangat sejuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya rasa berada di tempat teduh\Nakan menenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, saya sangat suka tempat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari sini...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya bisa melihat seluruh kediaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, Marie-2,\Ndan Tuan Roy ada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tempat yang paling berharga bagi saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya bisa mengistirahatkan tubuh dan pikiran saya di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie Evans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu di sini hanya karena pekerjaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, jika tempat ini terasa\Nseperti rumah bagimu, meski hanya sedikit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan sangat bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, ini adalah hari inspeksi\Nuntuk taman hiburan raksasa
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang sudah diatur sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai pewaris, beban kerja Arthur\Nmeningkat belakangan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie-2, Mode Kendaraan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Destiny Park sudah dekat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu, cepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur, kamu di sini.\NAku sudah menunggumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paman Rustin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian semua di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong bantuannya hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya, jangan menahan diri\Ndan silakan berbagi pendapat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Silakan berbagi pendapat"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berarti kita bisa langsung\Nmengekspresikan pendapat negatif
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang awalnya sulit dikatakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bibi Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu lama sekali, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tunanganmu, Isabel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunangan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia yang ada di episode delapan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan.\NJangan bicara omong kosong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bertunangan\Ndengan saudaraku, Maynard, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan Paman Carl\Ndan Bibi Charlotte mengakuinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu karena kamu lebih baik, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau menjadi pengantinmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar gadis kecil keras kepala.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bukan gadis kecil!\NUsiaku sudah 14 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, gadis ini bukan tunanganku.\NBukan apa-apa juga bagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Isabel, ini mahakarya Zetes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}robot pelayan berteknologi tinggi\Nuntuk keamanan bernama Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pasti manusia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu yang dikatakan intuisi wanitaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur, kamu ditipu olehnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil itu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar anak nakal!\NBeraninya kamu mengatakan omong kosong itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini waktu yang penting bagi Marie dan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini waktu yang penting bagi Marie dan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.95,0:09:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka bahkan menawarkan\Nsewa kostum Halloween sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia manis sekali...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gerbang detektor logam ini\Nbekerja dengan sangat baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini gawat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gerbang detektor logam\Ntak bereaksi terhadap Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka berdua robot perusahaan kami.\NWajar jika detektornya berbunyi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini besar sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, ini sangat besar\Nsampai aku tak tahu lokasi semua wahana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, karena kamu robot,\Nbuatlah peta taman hiburan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan tunjukkan jalannya\Npada Arthur dan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil aku bisa\Nmelakukan hal seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau naik roller coaster sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa denganmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bahkan tak bisa menunjukkan jalannya?\NMaka, pulanglah, dasar tidak berguna!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang harus kulakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beruntung!\NEntah siapa yang menjatuhkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Kunjungan Pertama?\NKuasai Taman dengan Peta Panduan Ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk Pemula Sungguhan."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tepat waktu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang dia lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan mendekatinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku ketahuan.\N- Luar biasa! Itu robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Roy, biarkan Marie-2\Nbermain dengan anak-anak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke taman hiburan mana pun kita pergi,\Nantrean roller coaster selalu panjang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus cepat mengantre!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur, cepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih cepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berputar lebih cepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga bisa terbang bebas di langit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu kita membeli Destiny Park,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mari produksi massal Marie-2\Nsebagai atraksi utama kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, Roy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa ada cara untuk membuat\Nsemua anak bahagia sekaligus?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, saya punya caranya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Roy, kamu memang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu berencana mengalihkan\Nbiaya pengembangan robot itu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ke Destiny Park, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda menyanjung saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang di Destiny Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau bermain dengan robot itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, Sayang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini menyenangkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, Arthur hanya menghabiskan waktu\Ndengan pelayan robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, dia tampak lelah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, apa yang harus\Nkita mainkan selanjutnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie harus mengisi ulang tenaga.\NMari istirahat sebentar lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Aku mau bermain!\NAku mau bermain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku! Mau! Bermain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, aku lelah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu terlalu muda\Nuntuk bersikap seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah itu Nyantaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah juga menyukainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan berfoto dengannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sangat berenergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, sekarang aku bisa\Nberduaan dengan Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku baik-baik saja. Jangan khawatir.\N- Anak-Anak, jangan coba ini di rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus membuat Marie minum air.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan meninggalkan ini di sini lalu pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Isabel juga tak ada di sini sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, tunggu aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau ke toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga, aku terlalu kenyang,\Njadi tak bisa minum itu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh minta tolong buangkan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, sayang sekali\Nkarena aku hampir tidak minum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Glek...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ciuman tidak langsung?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kamu lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu milik Arthur...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak pernah memercayaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesuai dugaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kamu tak mau aku memberi tahu\Nsiapa pun soal ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bantu agar aku bisa bersama Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ketahuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, maaf membuatmu menunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Isabel, kamu sudah kembali?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, silakan ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie sepertinya merasa lebih baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang aku akan membawa Anda ke tempat\NAnda bisa bermesraan dengan Nona Isabel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.18,0:14:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian tampak serasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian tampak serasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian tampak serasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa dengan Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang dia pikirkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa membaca emosinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat ini, Marie bersyukur\Ndia memiliki wajah datar alami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika dipikir-pikir,\Nseseorang seperti Tuan Arthur
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:15:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lebih cocok bersama wanita muda\Nseperti Nona Isabel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duniaku berbeda dengan Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu persis posisiku
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan itu cinta yang harus kurelakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, Tuan Arthur\Nsudah sangat baik padaku
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hingga aku melupakan\Nhal yang paling penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu, aku memutuskan untuk tetap\Ndi sisi Tuan Arthur dan melindunginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyembunyikan fakta bahwa aku manusia\Ndan mendukung cinta Isabel
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah misiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benci Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum bisa memberitahunya karena\NPaman Carl memperlakukanku dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, aku memberitahunya kali ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kubilang, "Aku benci orang\Nyang terus bersikap seperti anak manja."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika terus begini,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}cinta Nona Isabel akan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Nona Isabel.\N- Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana bisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Isabel, apa Anda terluka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada tebing di depan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah membantuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin lebih baik\Naku merelakan cinta ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Isabel, terlalu dini untuk menyerah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dibandingkan dengan saya,\Nyang menipu Tuan Arthur,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda bisa melakukan\Nlebih banyak daripada saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal menyerah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pikirkan itu setelah Anda melakukan\Nsemua yang Anda bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, tolong jangan terlihat sedih.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sangat baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tak perlu repot-repot\Ndengan anak nakal sepertiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, ayo kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya di sini tidak aman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini... Sebenarnya aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie! Isabel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie! Isabel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, Isabel, krisis sudah teratasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerja bagus, Semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, Nona Isabel,\Ntolong berbaikanlah dengan Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika sungguh menyukainya,\NAnda harus jujur dan mengatakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah cukup, Isabel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu punya perasaan aneh\Ntentang kasih sayangmu padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Isabel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tak punya perasaan\Nuntukku sama sekali, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu hanya mencintai Maynard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat aku pertama bertemu,\Nkalian sangat akrab.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kita belum pernah bicara,\Nkamu tiba-tiba menyatakan cintamu padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mengira kamu tipe orang\Nyang bisa cepat berubah perasaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa, Isabel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang kucintai adalah Tuan Maynard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sungguh orang yang baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, saat itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah mengadakan pesta setiap pekan.\NMenyebalkan sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika tak bersikap seperti perempuan,\Naku akan dimarahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku suka memanjat pohon, tapi katanya,\N"Aneh jika seorang gadis melakukan itu."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kamu putri Paman Rustin, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Maynard.\NKamu suka memanjat pohon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga.\NMari bermain bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pohon di sana lebih besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, sejak kamu datang,\NTuan Maynard berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mengambil posisi pewaris
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan kini dia hanya memikirkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bahkan tak mau melihatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya kupikir\Njika aku dekat dengan Arthur,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin Tuan Maynard\Nakhirnya akan memperhatikanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika dia bisa melihatku lagi,\Naku mau memberitahunya,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Tak peduli berapa banyak orang luar biasa\Nyang datang,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu akan selalu menjadi\Nyang terbaik di hatiku."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hatsyi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menang kali ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya Tuan Maynard\Nsangat payah dalam poker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Empat kartu sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tak terlihat\Nseperti punya kartu seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian semua membohongiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama dengan pembunuh sumpitan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya Arthur sudah dia habisi,\Njadi aku bahagia untuk sesaat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, Arthur masih hidup dan sehat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda menyewa\Npembunuh kelas tiga dan gagal lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sangat menyebalkan! Diam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo main lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini terjadi sebagian karena salahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang benar jika aku tidak muncul,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}keadaan mungkin tak akan berakhir\Nseperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh minta maaf\Nsudah merepotkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:21:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah itu saudara tiriku atau kamu,\Nseharusnya aku menghadapinya dengan benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Itu menyenangkan.\N- Ya, mari datang ke sini lagi besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang harus kulakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.94,0:21:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berbaikan dengan Isabel,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.82,0:21:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dia tahu rahasiaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu robot,\Njadi kamu mungkin tak mengerti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meminum barang orang lain\Ntanpa izin adalah kejahatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menuju tak terbatas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja, Isabel masih anak-anak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa dibilang mereka berdua sama persis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.11,0:21:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu kecil dan jauh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya menyenangkan sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa semuanya bisa berakhir seperti ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:22:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya mau menonton episode berikutnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.81,0:23:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.02,0:23:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengesampingkan\Nmomen orang mesum mujurnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.87,0:23:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ceritanya tiba-tiba berubah jadi serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kamu?
